 *      -> the Tx led turns on and after 3 s it flashes very fast (20 Hz)
 * 6. Release the Pairing button
 *      -> after a few seconds Rx and Tx leds start flashing slowly (0.5 Hz) : Rx & Tx are paired and transmitting data
 
